#. <section class="sutta" id="sn20.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn20.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 20"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 20"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.12:0.2"
msgid "1. Opammavagga"
msgstr "1. Similes"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn20.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Dutiyasiṅgālasutta"
msgstr "12. A Jackal"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn20.12:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Assuttha no tumhe, bhikkhave, rattiyā paccūsasamayaṃ jarasiṅgālassa "
"vassamānassā”ti?"
msgstr "“Mendicants, did you hear an old jackal howling at the crack of dawn?”"

msgctxt "sn20.12:1.3"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”."
msgstr "“Yes, sir.”"

msgctxt "sn20.12:1.4"
msgid ""
"“Siyā kho, bhikkhave, tasmiṃ jarasiṅgāle yā kāci kataññutā kataveditā, na "
"tveva idhekacce sakyaputtiyapaṭiññe siyā yā kāci kataññutā kataveditā."
msgstr ""
"“There might be some gratitude and thankfulness in that old jackal, but "
"there is none in a certain person here who claims to be a follower of the "
"Sakyan son."

msgctxt "sn20.12:1.5"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "sn20.12:1.6"
msgid "‘kataññuno bhavissāma katavedino;"
msgstr "‘We will be grateful and thankful."

#. VAR: no → na ca noti idaṃ bj, pts1-2 potthakesu
#. VAR: nassissatī’ti → mā nassissatīti (bj, pts1-2) | ca na sissatīti (s1) | vinasissatīti (s2, s3, km)
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.7"
msgid "na ca no amhesu appakampi kataṃ nassissatī’ti."
msgstr "We won’t forget even a small thing done for us.’"

msgctxt "sn20.12:1.8"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr "That’s how you should train.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.9"
msgid "Dvādasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.12:1.10"
msgid "Opammavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn20.12:2.1"
msgid "Kūṭaṃ nakhasikhaṃ kulaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn20.12:2.2"
msgid "okkhā satti dhanuggaho;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn20.12:2.3"
msgid "Āṇi kaliṅgaro nāgo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn20.12:2.4"
msgid "biḷāro dve siṅgālakāti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "sn20.12:2.5"
msgid "Opammasaṃyuttaṃ samattaṃ."
msgstr "The Linked Discourses with similes are complete."
